        "titolo_orig": "Saudi Arabia opens Hajj packages booking for domestic pilgrims with strict payment timeline",
        "testo_it": "L'Arabia Saudita apre le prenotazioni per l'Hajj ai pellegrini residenti con scadenze di pagamento rigide.",
        "priorita": "Bassa",
        "id_gruppo": 15,
        "link": "https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-opens-hajj-packages-booking-for-domestic-pilgrims-with-strict-payment-timeline/articleshow/129070606.cms",
        "orario": "06:26",
